fields.name: Kirtan
fields.description: The Kirtan program at Gobind Sarvar incorporates all aspects of Kirtan and Gurbani to allow students to experience Guru Sahib's teachings at a much deeper level. Currently we offer 10 levels of Harmonium, 5 levels of Tabla and 3 levels of String Instruments (Dilruba, Rabaab, Sarandaa, Sitar, and Sarangee) instruction.

fields.name: Little Khalsa Club
fields.description: Little Khalsa Club (LKC) is a unique class for 3-6 year old students which was started in September 2013 due to high demand after a very successful Little Gursikhs Summer Camp. The core focus of LKC is to encourage students to begin building lasting friendships while learning the beauty of Guru Sahib's Path at a very young age.
